## This file is where you should list any debian/linux
## packages that your project depends on. We will read
## them when building the docker image, and we expect
## one (AND ONLY ONE) package per line. For example:
##
##     # file: apt-packages.list
##     libxrender
##     libgcc
##     libapache2
##
## Note that we will attempt to install all packages
## at once when bulding the docker image, and if
## any one package fails to install, the entire step
## will fail. So make sure your list is accurate.
##
## To search for your package, search online:
##     debian-testing libapache2
## or you can open the text list here:
##     https://packages.debian.org/testing/allpackages?format=txt.gz
## and search it with 'CTRL + f'
